## Limitations

The findings are based on subjective accounts and personal essays, which may not represent the broader population. Additionally, the sources vary in credibility, with some being personal blogs or community forums. The lack of empirical data limits the generalizability of the conclusions drawn. Further research with a more scientific approach could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.

